org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model

Interface URLImageComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Component
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    URLImageComponentImpl

    public interface URLImageComponent
extends Component
    A representation of the model object 'URL Image Component'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Descriptor
    • Image Url
    • Fallback Image Url
    • Width
    • Height

    See Also:
    DetailViewPackage.getURLImageComponent()
